dc_description_s: Crawford County, Pennsylvania address points. Location and information of address points in Crawford County,Pennsylvania. This feature service has restricted fields available for this open data version. Certain fields have been redacted. The full dataset (as seen via the GIS mapping applications) is available via cost by contacting Crawford County. The full dataset available at cost provides all records that are not redacted by law. This is a feature service and data can change at anytime without notice.
